1
00:00:13,880 --> 00:00:14,880
Where did this wildflower come from?

2
00:00:14,900 --> 00:00:15,560
Don't touch it.

3
00:00:16,880 --> 00:00:19,210
You're treating this like it's a treasure.

4
00:00:19,540 --> 00:00:20,580
Let me tell you,

5
00:00:21,260 --> 00:00:23,120
Yi Qiuting's old flame

6
00:00:23,470 --> 00:00:25,860
attempted suicide and was hospitalized.

7
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:31,400
I'm talking to you.

8
00:00:31,430 --> 00:00:33,110
Why don't you react at all?

9
00:00:33,870 --> 00:00:35,040
With her making such a fuss,

10
00:00:35,140 --> 00:00:37,730
Yi Qiuting's attention will be even more on her.

11
00:00:37,840 --> 00:00:39,820
Listen, you need to have a sense of crisis.

12
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:42,320
Please leave.

13
00:00:42,780 --> 00:00:44,030
A sense of crisis.

14
00:00:44,410 --> 00:00:45,700
Alright, I'm leaving.

15
00:01:02,310 --> 00:01:05,379
Blue veins are for slow blood flow;

16
00:01:05,820 --> 00:01:07,740
cutting here usually won't cause death.

17
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:11,220
In 10 minutes, Leng Mei will come in to deliver food.

18
00:01:11,910 --> 00:01:12,990
It's about time.

19
00:01:20,910 --> 00:01:22,120
Why did you do this?

20
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,160
Why are you being so foolish?

21
00:01:39,140 --> 00:01:41,610
Yes, I am foolish.

22
00:01:42,950 --> 00:01:45,210
I attempted suicide because I couldn't get the love I wanted.

23
00:01:47,930 --> 00:01:49,890
You want me to say I'm sorry?

24
00:01:52,110 --> 00:01:55,570
No, the one who should say sorry is me.

25
00:01:58,390 --> 00:01:59,680
I shouldn't have

26
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:02,160
let you take off your armor of pride for me.

27
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:05,440
I should have listened to you

28
00:02:05,740 --> 00:02:07,560
to be someone without independent thoughts

29
00:02:07,580 --> 00:02:08,820
or personality.

30
00:02:11,180 --> 00:02:12,660
I should have lived

31
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,010
in the love cage

32
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:15,560
you built for me,

33
00:02:15,990 --> 00:02:17,290
as your pet,

34
00:02:18,140 --> 00:02:19,740
accepting all your joys and angers.

35
00:02:20,770 --> 00:02:22,570
I failed your love.

36
00:02:24,540 --> 00:02:27,570
Now all I have is hatred.

37
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:33,430
No, you don't hate me.

38
00:02:35,860 --> 00:02:37,560
You saved me.

39
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:40,010
You said you loved me.

40
00:02:40,220 --> 00:02:42,579
You also said you would never leave me.

41
00:02:42,610 --> 00:02:43,570
Yi Qiuting,

42
00:02:44,010 --> 00:02:45,210
you still don't know

43
00:02:45,230 --> 00:02:46,470
why you are wrong?

44
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:51,380
Our relationship is over.

45
00:02:52,020 --> 00:02:53,000
Please let me go.

46
00:02:55,390 --> 00:02:59,930
Zhao Xingrou, I will never let go.

47
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:02,340
Say you love me.

48
00:03:04,130 --> 00:03:04,770
Say it!

49
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:10,000
Please, say it.

50
00:03:21,770 --> 00:03:23,530
One day when you say it,

51
00:03:23,990 --> 00:03:25,720
I'll give you freedom.

52
00:03:28,110 --> 00:03:28,750
Keep an eye on her.

53
00:03:28,780 --> 00:03:29,520
Yes.

54
00:03:32,340 --> 00:03:37,460
[Blazing Elegance]

55
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:37,460
[Episode 6]

56
00:03:42,900 --> 00:03:44,040
I'm sorry.

57
00:03:44,070 --> 00:03:45,870
Watch where you're going. What's the rush?

58
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:47,070
I'm sorry.

59
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,700
Don't linger here. Get lost!

60
00:03:50,740 --> 00:03:51,950
Leaving now.

61
00:04:01,900 --> 00:04:02,690
Where have you been?

62
00:04:02,900 --> 00:04:04,070
The newspaper office.

63
00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:05,680
Weren't you following me the whole time?

64
00:04:06,060 --> 00:04:07,220
And after the newspaper office?

65
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,190
Lieutenant Peng,

66
00:04:10,020 --> 00:04:13,470
why should I report my whereabouts to you?

67
00:04:13,860 --> 00:04:14,810
Who are you to me?

68
00:04:16,579 --> 00:04:19,310
There's only one person in this world who can control me,

69
00:04:20,350 --> 00:04:22,790
and that's my wife.

70
00:04:24,350 --> 00:04:25,600
Stay away from me.

71
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:31,600
If anyone's leaving, it's you. This is my home.

72
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:44,270
Is there anything else?

73
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,510
Didn't you say before

74
00:04:45,530 --> 00:04:47,020
that you wanted me to help you transcribe your novel?

75
00:04:53,900 --> 00:04:56,200
Sure, have a seat.

76
00:04:58,030 --> 00:05:00,650
At the Cuihua Pavilion Courtesan Competition,

77
00:05:00,790 --> 00:05:03,770
men spending fortunes.

78
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:24,210
Flowers carpeting both banks of the Qinhuai River, lights blazing.

79
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:27,370
It's the annual grand event of romance,

80
00:05:27,730 --> 00:05:29,550
the Courtesan Competition,

81
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:31,610
Young men from all over the country

82
00:05:31,630 --> 00:05:32,680
flock here,

83
00:05:33,190 --> 00:05:36,000
just to witness with their own eyes a peerless beauty

84
00:05:36,380 --> 00:05:39,580
standing out from thousands of women.

85
00:06:01,300 --> 00:06:02,060
I'm sorry.

86
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:10,560
[Cheng Xun]

87
00:06:40,260 --> 00:06:42,680
My name is Wu Chongmo.

88
00:06:42,740 --> 00:06:43,440
Go away.

89
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,570
I don't want to talk to you right now.

90
00:06:49,300 --> 00:06:51,330
Let's drink together in this chance meeting.

91
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:54,080
Tonight, let's just drink, nothing else.

92
00:07:07,060 --> 00:07:08,550
Everyone has troubles.

93
00:07:09,740 --> 00:07:11,520
Even someone as carefree as Li Bai

94
00:07:11,860 --> 00:07:13,770
would drink alone without company.

95
00:07:14,970 --> 00:07:16,040
Li Bai?

96
00:07:18,470 --> 00:07:20,050
I won't end up like him,

97
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:21,600
becoming a loner.

98
00:07:22,830 --> 00:07:24,570
I will keep her by my side,

99
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:27,090
no matter what it takes.

100
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:30,510
To keep someone, what else do you know

101
00:07:30,990 --> 00:07:31,750
besides violence and oppression?

102
00:07:32,770 --> 00:07:34,280
I don't need you to teach me.

103
00:07:34,300 --> 00:07:37,080
Then who do you need to teach you? Your father?

104
00:07:39,020 --> 00:07:42,800
He'll only teach you to be selfish and brutal,

105
00:07:43,300 --> 00:07:46,020
treating others' dignity and lives as worthless.

106
00:07:46,690 --> 00:07:48,930
Don't you dare mention him.

107
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,600
Everyone is afraid of him,

108
00:07:51,860 --> 00:07:53,930
but he doesn't understand love at all.

109
00:07:55,870 --> 00:07:56,630
I do.

110
00:07:57,740 --> 00:08:00,810
I have a wonderful woman

111
00:08:03,410 --> 00:08:05,570
who loves me very, very much.

112
00:08:07,980 --> 00:08:10,290
Alright, good for you.

113
00:08:10,860 --> 00:08:13,110
Cheers to having someone who loves you.

114
00:08:25,460 --> 00:08:26,850
Don't touch me. Don't touch me!

115
00:08:27,450 --> 00:08:28,600
What's wrong with you?

116
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:36,039
Go and ask Miss Duan to come here.

117
00:08:36,070 --> 00:08:36,630
Yes.

118
00:08:43,789 --> 00:08:44,910
How did I fall asleep?

119
00:08:46,190 --> 00:08:50,570
Lieutenant Peng, you've been busy all day. It's normal to be tired.

120
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:52,890
How long have I been asleep?

121
00:08:54,220 --> 00:08:55,220
For a while now.

122
00:09:01,220 --> 00:09:02,260
Aunt.

123
00:09:03,140 --> 00:09:04,230
Jinyao.

124
00:09:05,010 --> 00:09:06,380
Qiuting is drunk.

125
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:08,340
You stay here tonight

126
00:09:08,370 --> 00:09:09,600
and take good care of him.

127
00:09:10,010 --> 00:09:12,280
Aunt, a man and a woman alone togetherâ€”

128
00:09:12,310 --> 00:09:13,830
it's not appropriate.

129
00:09:14,110 --> 00:09:15,440
Don't worry,

130
00:09:15,570 --> 00:09:17,620
you two are getting married soon.

131
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:20,990
Even if you get pregnant now, it's legitimate.

132
00:09:21,550 --> 00:09:22,470
Aunt.

133
00:09:22,490 --> 00:09:24,870
Don't be shy. Go upstairs now.

134
00:09:35,030 --> 00:09:35,940
Xingrou.

135
00:09:39,420 --> 00:09:40,450
Xingrou.

136
00:09:42,470 --> 00:09:44,510
How am I inferior to Zhao Xingrou?

137
00:09:45,910 --> 00:09:47,400
Why are you so reluctant

138
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:48,470
to even make a deal with me?

139
00:09:48,930 --> 00:09:50,210
Xingrou.

140
00:09:55,140 --> 00:09:56,340
Xingrou.

141
00:09:57,440 --> 00:10:00,950
Perhaps tonight is my only chance.

142
00:10:01,450 --> 00:10:04,140
I've endured so much humiliation and grievance.

143
00:10:04,470 --> 00:10:07,470
I can't let Zhao Xingrou get pregnant before me.

144
00:10:18,710 --> 00:10:19,730
Xingrou.

145
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,940
Let's have a baby of our own, okay?

146
00:10:29,820 --> 00:10:31,050
You're not Xingrou!

147
00:10:32,170 --> 00:10:34,500
Go away! Leave now!

148
00:11:06,820 --> 00:11:08,790
Qiuting, you're awake.

149
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:14,360
What are you doing here?

150
00:11:17,290 --> 00:11:19,320
You were drunk last night.

151
00:11:19,340 --> 00:11:20,930
Aunt asked me to take care of you.

152
00:11:22,180 --> 00:11:23,590
And then you...

153
00:11:29,730 --> 00:11:31,540
Why are you looking at me like that?

154
00:11:34,330 --> 00:11:37,610
Alright, I'll take responsibility for you.

155
00:11:46,340 --> 00:11:49,550
[Keep quiet]

156
00:12:05,620 --> 00:12:06,420
Where is she?

157
00:12:18,330 --> 00:12:19,070
Young Master Cheng.

158
00:12:21,510 --> 00:12:22,380
Please follow me.

159
00:12:23,860 --> 00:12:28,150
[Ward One]

160
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,690
It's time for Miss Zhao's injection.

161
00:12:44,530 --> 00:12:45,490
Xingrou.

162
00:12:45,620 --> 00:12:46,880
-Change your clothes. 
-Cheng Xun.

163
00:12:47,740 --> 00:12:49,190
How did you know I was in the hospital?

164
00:12:49,210 --> 00:12:50,100
I don't know either.

165
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:51,480
Someone sent me a letter.

166
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:52,940
Who was it?

167
00:12:53,140 --> 00:12:54,100
It doesn't matter who.

168
00:12:54,860 --> 00:12:56,840
Xingrou, I've arranged a boat.

169
00:12:56,860 --> 00:12:58,550
We'll leave Hangcheng tonight.

170
00:12:59,810 --> 00:13:00,460
Okay.

171
00:13:23,420 --> 00:13:24,080
Young Marshal,

172
00:13:24,370 --> 00:13:25,630
Cheng Xun's passenger ship

173
00:13:25,690 --> 00:13:27,180
was supposed to depart at 10 last night,

174
00:13:27,310 --> 00:13:28,630
but due to rough seas,

175
00:13:28,650 --> 00:13:29,880
he changed to leave by train.

176
00:13:30,370 --> 00:13:32,210
Gather everyone and follow me.

177
00:13:35,170 --> 00:13:36,130
Search!

178
00:13:42,470 --> 00:13:43,070
Go.

179
00:13:46,730 --> 00:13:47,730
Let's go.

180
00:13:47,790 --> 00:13:48,360
Hurry up, let's go.

181
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:49,440
Where's Xingrou?

182
00:13:51,170 --> 00:13:52,050
Speak up!

183
00:13:52,620 --> 00:13:55,760
Yi Qiuting, you've gone to great lengths,

184
00:13:56,260 --> 00:13:59,340
but I'm afraid it's all been in vain.

185
00:14:02,030 --> 00:14:03,190
What do you mean?

186
00:14:04,660 --> 00:14:06,390
Xingrou didn't leave with me.

187
00:14:11,770 --> 00:14:12,650
Xingrou.

188
00:14:14,310 --> 00:14:15,780
We'll leave Hangcheng tonight,

189
00:14:15,810 --> 00:14:17,560
first to southeast Asia, then to Europe,

190
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:18,960
and leave here forever.

191
00:14:20,880 --> 00:14:24,320
Cheng Xun, thank you for rescuing me,

192
00:14:24,790 --> 00:14:25,910
and thank you for your kindness.

193
00:14:27,190 --> 00:14:28,880
But you have your own ideals and ambitions,

194
00:14:29,390 --> 00:14:30,380
and I don't want to live

195
00:14:30,410 --> 00:14:31,770
a life arranged by others anymore.

196
00:14:34,510 --> 00:14:36,440
Wish you all the best abroad.

197
00:14:39,310 --> 00:14:39,910
Take care.

198
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:51,210
I don't know where she went either.

199
00:15:08,190 --> 00:15:11,820
Xingrou, you better hide well.

200
00:15:13,310 --> 00:15:15,010
I'm coming to find you.
